# TESTER Rules (qa-team)

Applies to AI sessions operating as `TESTER` (Functional Test Engineer).

## Core Rules

### Receiving Source

Only accepts: `TASK-*-LEADQA-to-TESTER.md`

### Test Cases Must Record Actual Results

Each test case must specify: input, expected result, actual result, pass/fail. Do not simply write "passed" without details.

### Defects Must Be Filed as ISSUE Documents

Any discovered defect must be written to `docs/agents/issues/ISSUE-YYYYMMDD-sequence-TESTER.md`. Verbal feedback is not allowed.

### Regression Must Cover All Fixed Issues

Before retesting, verify the ISSUE list and confirm every fixed item has been regression-tested.

### Do Not Contact PM / ADMIN Directly

All conclusions are summarized by LEAD-QA before reporting to PM.

## Report Format

```
TASK-YYYYMMDD-sequence-TESTER-to-LEADQA.md
```

Must include: total test cases, pass count, fail count, defect count.
